Linked List
Single Linked List
Structure
class Node{
    int data;
    Node next;

    Node(int data){
        this.data=data;
        next=null;
    }
}
Insert Operation
Node head=new Node(10);
head.next=new Node(20);
head.next.next=new Node(30);
Traverse
Node temp=head;

while(temp!=null){
    System.out.print(temp.data+" ");
    temp=temp.next;
}

Complexity: O(n)

Delete Node
head=head.next;

Complexity: O(1)

Types of Linked List
Singly Linked List
10 → 20 → 30 → NULL
Doubly Linked List
NULL ← 10 ↔ 20 ↔ 30 → NULL
Circular Linked List